Servers.ServerMessage: Programmers in China launched an online campaign against [implicitly forced overtime work](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/996_working_hour_system) in pursuit of balanced work-life relationship. Sshwifty wouldn't exist if its author must work such extreme hours. If you're benefiting from hobbyist projects like this one, please consider to support the action.
